Qaddafi Hires South African Lawyers for Possible Defense, Times Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-31T04:56:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/qaddafi-hires-south-african-lawyers-for-possible-defense-times-reports.html
Libyan leader  Muammar Qaddafi  has
hired  South Africa ’s Langa Attorneys to defend him and senior
officials in his government against any charges that the
 International Criminal Court  may bring against them,
Johannesburg’s Times newspaper reported, citing a person close
to discussions.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
